{"tid":1860312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭係全香港最黃嗰個","createTime":"2020-02-03T14:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T16:09:59.000Z","uid":339159,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"84b46a5fa282413298d5cf99e822d560103363f3","tid":1860312,"uid":339159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"呢十一個月以黎，一直用各種手段各種途徑欺壓香港人，應該唔需要再重覆敘述<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎事件，我覺得係成個抗爭既endgame<br />\n不封關，不關注醫護人員，不設立任何防疫措施⋯口罩⋯各樣那樣根本唔洗我再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭做到呢步已經唔再關民主.自由事，係牽涉到我地生命安危，點解你仲可以唔擺工，俾全世界睇到香港人係極權下奪回我地應有嘅權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭已經做到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，全港大擺工就等於Ironman snap fingers,做唔做就睇我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYnTTpT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYnTTpT.jpg&h=faee3c6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91928323aa59b9b4b92242725ce252b041672c14","tid":1860312,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:49:37.000Z","msg":"攬炒之母"},{"pid":"d78171cde881a1e6dd12591a3bdd994d589f3af7","tid":1860312,"uid":313072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"教母"},{"pid":"2a27f1578d658fd055d77466cd5a1f635991a5fd","tid":1860312,"uid":2526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好咁講<br />\n好多藍絲已經開始割<br />\n話林鄭其實係黃絲，有心搞死香港<br />\n龍門真係任佢地擺<br />\n好撚無賴"},{"pid":"61eeae1404636b3af485fc557fde52927a22dac7","tid":1860312,"uid":42223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"邊個叫佢下台，邊個就係鬼<br />\n唔係9月點贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236176c03fca2dd841b31985792277289ab7a1b4","tid":1860